{"tid":1453483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[求whistle blower] 給TVB新聞部離職良心員工","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T05:31:21.000Z","uid":269288,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"856bffb2edaec0495f1df575130d05aa48703711","tid":1453483,"uid":269288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"首先，送上敬意！<br />\n<br />\n但離職之前，能否先搜集、整理tvb打壓新聞自由，製造假新聞的罪證，公開給公眾知道？我地需要你地手上既黑材料呀！好人一生平安！<br />\n<br />\n今個星期是屬於機場和罷工的。請大家準備好彈藥，下一輪爆tvb大鑊啦，好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n支持良心新聞工作者<br />\n幫我推到佢地睇到，唔該"},{"pid":"77ac815a756c86bbcc21f78c6da88408e71deecc","tid":1453483,"uid":146521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"啱呀"},{"pid":"8fb103b1cfe9147d63df3f0ad17471a86130403f","tid":1453483,"uid":3239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:26:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"171acbb776098992a22be33aaf5181202ef056a6","tid":1453483,"uid":174936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096280af9ba2d33d79afc1c90a44ebb02444fe56","tid":1453483,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:37:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港需要人道救援</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當下，香港極需要不受滋擾的中立醫療團隊。我們需要無國界醫生、聯合國維和部隊，以及其他人道救援組織。只有他們可以為香港提供正常醫療保障，免於中共香港警察滋擾。以下這個聯署，是要求美國派遣醫療船以提供中立的醫療服務。美國醫療船扺達後，其他國際醫療組織就更易來港協助，以減低香港人在今次戰爭的傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n這是十分實際的要求，也是極為急切和重要。為免香港發生大規模人道災難，請各位簽署並廣傳！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpD11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=916b61e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster</a>"},{"pid":"70bf26449f9ffc59c2c13d73e01ee25b9ce4f7e8","tid":1453483,"uid":269288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"推到佢地睇到"},{"pid":"38232fa7dc6713a34593570610b1aaba22ed9686","tid":1453483,"uid":269288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:07:38.000Z","msg":"有無真身？求你地了"},{"pid":"2c79f891e028b43d4b62bfcbe37ae6421ca917eb","tid":1453483,"uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:07:55.000Z","msg":"想整合一個良心小店white list<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1453940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1453940</a>"},{"pid":"7a06e5aac8af185e79147aa32046660fb6f733ea","tid":1453483,"uid":269288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:12:42.000Z","msg":"有無人識佢地，傳畀佢地睇"},{"pid":"4e06b9f3286c88435b78809d4b4742dc3808b598","tid":1453483,"uid":269288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:04:28.000Z","msg":"實有人識架嘛？"},{"pid":"1b8424c1b1332ac3ba6aea9f9f3af25c04f54fc9","tid":1453483,"uid":269288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:41:43.000Z","msg":"無人識"},{"pid":"ea86b1181352d17c99d011464d865bcb941b1162","tid":1453483,"uid":269288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:31:21.000Z","msg":"辭哂仲未有人爆料"}]}